{"type":"message","id":"b9d54426","parentId":"72f23352","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:34:41.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The gateway daemon runs in WSL — it's always online even when your TUI session is closed. Think of it like a background service. When you message me on WhatsApp, it routes through that daemon to me. Your laptop being off doesn't matter because the daemon is running on the WSL instance, which is separate from whether you have a terminal open.\n\nThe TUI is just one interface — WhatsApp works independently. Same way a server doesn't need you logged in to keep serving web pages."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":28482,"output":324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28806,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775277281641}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c05cfeb","parentId":"b9d54426","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:34:41.780Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The gateway daemon runs in WSL — it's always online even when your TUI session is closed. Think of it like a background service. When you message me on WhatsApp, it routes through that daemon to me. Your laptop being off doesn't matter because the daemon is running on the WSL instance, which is separate from whether you have a terminal open.\n\nThe TUI is just one interface — WhatsApp works independently. Same way a server doesn't need you logged in to keep serving web pages."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775277281779}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b39c369","parentId":"4c05cfeb","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:34:42.036Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3EB0C6A9D21B49733DC885\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+27763674298\",\n  \"sender\": \"+27763674298\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"+27763674298\",\n  \"id\": \"+27763674298\",\n  \"e164\": \"+27763674298\"\n}\n```\n\nThe gateway daemon runs in WSL — it's always online even when your TUI session is closed. Think of it like a background service. When you message me on WhatsApp, it routes through that daemon to me. Your laptop being off doesn't matter because the daemon is running on the WSL instance, which is separate from whether you have a terminal open.\n\nThe TUI is just one interface — WhatsApp works independently. Same way a server doesn't need you logged in to keep serving web pages."}],"timestamp":1775277282029}}
