{"type":"message","id":"f24c7fc9","parentId":"c022add8","timestamp":"2026-04-04T04:40:39.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nIt IS set up — ran last night at midnight SAST. Job ID `4ee0c18c` (\"Dream Mode — Nightly Reflection\"), fires every night at midnight. It's an isolated session that reads yesterday's session, distills key decisions/lessons/reminders into memory files.\n\nRan OK last night (248 seconds, status: ok). But I say this honestly — I don't know if the output was actually useful. It writes to the daily memory file but I haven't compared it to just writing my own end-of-day notes.\n\nWere you expecting something different from it? Like a morning briefing delivered to you? Because right now it just writes to the memory file silently. I could set it to announce results to you on WhatsApp at 8am or something if that's the workflow you wanted."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":37372,"output":481,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37853,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775277639228}}
