{"type":"message","id":"f1bb7a03","parentId":"24c13929","timestamp":"2026-04-05T00:04:16.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_e5bd5f8b-37a7-4c74-b4fb-fd72e4ad5dcd","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Git Repository — Dawn Workspace\n\n## Remote\n**No remote currently set.** \nThe workspace git repo is local-only. If you want to back it up to GitHub/GitLab:\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\ngit remote add origin https://github.com/<user>/<repo>.git\ngit push -u origin master\n```\n\n## Branch\n- `master` — main working branch\n\n## Last Commit\n```\n47b10e3 Audit: verify 2026-03-27 note compliance + add never-batch rule to AGENTS.md\n```\n\n## Recent Commit History (last 20 commits)\n| Commit | Message |\n|--------|---------|\n| 47b10e3 | Audit: verify 2026-03-27 note compliance + add never-batch rule to AGENTS.md |\n| 6da4dcc | Apr 5 00:29 - daily checkpoint |\n| 7963afb | Apr 4: USER.md update + sprint check-in 16:20 |\n| d012b4b | Sprint check-in 2026-04-04 12:04 SAST |\n| cf3541e | Sprint check-in 2026-04-04 10:03 SAST |\n| 9fada0e | Sprint check-in 2026-04-04 08:03 SAST |\n| ee4c678 | Sprint check-in 2026-04-04 04:03 SAST |\n| ff51c75 | Apr 3 afternoon flush: post series status, TinyQE results, research prompt v2 |\n| 77bc44f | Apr 3 full flush: session recovery, research prompt v2, LI032 draft, outstanding items |\n| abdf60d | Apr 4 morning: idle overnight, status clean |\n| daeab8b | Apr 3 evening: prompt v2, LI032 draft, deep research ready |\n| 34f3a3d | Apr 3 evening commit: prompt v2, li032/x032 drafts, tinyqe runs |\n| a760eea | Dream Mode Apr 4: Distill Apr 2 audit + Apr 3 work insights |\n| 8370149 | Apr 3 session close: TinyQE, post series draft, research prompt v2, gateway issues |\n| d634bf6 | Apr 3 afternoon flush: post series pitched, prompt fixed, research V2 ready |\n| 12d9914 | Apr 3 midday: draft posts, corrected research prompt, afternoon state |\n| 57bac7b | Sprint 14:03 — research prompt v2 done, drafts staged, awaiting Gemini reports |\n| 85d65cf | Sprint 12:30 — Apr 2 uncaptured feedback, morning routine state |\n| a293841 | Sprint check-in: Apr 3 08:03 SAST - morning routine state, daily memory update |\n| f9198b3 | Sprint check-in 2026-04-03 02:05 SAST — TrnsBank 175, restore kit done |\n\n## Backup Note\nThis repo has no remote. On restore to a new machine, either:\n1. Set up a new remote and push if you have one\n2. Keep it as a local-only repo\n3. Initialize a fresh git in the restored workspace if you don't need history\n\n## Files Excluded from Backup\nThe following were NOT included in the workspace backup (too large or machine-specific):\n- `.git/` — repo is local-only, no remote to push to\n- `rag/.venv/` — Python virtual environment (rebuild with pip)\n- `browser_profiles/` — browser session data (session-specific)\n- `playwright*` — browser automation cache\n- `node_modules/` — reinstalled by npm\n- `memory/` — backed up separately to `memory_backup/`\n","path":"/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/OneDrive/Apps/Dawn-Restore/GIT_REPO.md"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":55257,"output":875,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1775347456922}}
